"     Continuum of Depth of Sedation: Definition of General Anesthesia and Levels of Sedation/Analgesia. American Society of Anesthesiologists Standards, Guidelines, adb Statements, October 27, 2004 (file://www.asahq.org/publicationsAndServices/sgstoc.htm).",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?37/0/37893/abstract/16\">",
"      Chung SA, Yuan H, Chung F. A systemic review of obstructive sleep apnea and its implications for anesthesiologists. Anesth Analg 2008; 107:1543.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
